'''Suisio''' is a ''[[comune]]'' (municipality) in the [[Province of Bergamo]] in the [[Italy|Italian]] region of [[Lombardy]], located about 35&nbsp;km northeast of [[Milan]] and about 14&nbsp;km southwest of [[Bergamo]]. As of 31 December 2004, it had a population of 3,614 and an area of 4.6&nbsp;km<U+00B2>.<ref name="istat">All demographics and other statistics: Italian statistical institute [[National Institute of Statistics (Italy)|Istat]].</ref>

Suisio borders the following municipalities: [[Bottanuco]], [[Chignolo d'Isola]], [[Cornate d'Adda]], [[Medolago]].

